sql_query.sql: SELECT MAX(user_badges.id) AS id, MAX(user_badges.badge_id) AS badge_id, MAX(user_badges.user_id) AS user_id, MAX(user_badges.granted_at) AS granted_at, MAX(user_badges.granted_by_id) AS granted_by_id, MAX(user_badges.post_id) AS post_id, MAX(user_badges.notification_id) AS notification_id, MAX(user_badges.seq) AS seq, MAX(user_badges.featured_rank) AS featured_rank, MAX(user_badges.created_at) AS created_at, COUNT(*) AS "count" FROM "user_badges" WHERE "user_badges"."user_id" = 1242 AND (user_badges.badge_id IN (SELECT id FROM badges WHERE enabled)) AND (featured_rank <= 3) GROUP BY "user_badges"."badge_id", "user_badges"."user_id" ORDER BY MAX(featured_rank) ASC

sql_query.sql:
SELECT "groups"."id", "groups"."name", "groups"."created_at", "groups"."updated_at", "groups"."automatic", "groups"."user_count", "groups"."automatic_membership_email_domains", "groups"."primary_group", "groups"."title", "groups"."grant_trust_level", "groups"."incoming_email", "groups"."has_messages", "groups"."flair_bg_color", "groups"."flair_color", "groups"."bio_raw", "groups"."bio_cooked", "groups"."allow_membership_requests", "groups"."full_name", "groups"."default_notification_level", "groups"."visibility_level", "groups"."public_exit", "groups"."public_admission", "groups"."membership_request_template", "groups"."messageable_level", "groups"."mentionable_level", "groups"."publish_read_state", "groups"."members_visibility_level", "groups"."flair_icon", "groups"."flair_upload_id" FROM "groups" INNER JOIN "group_users" ON "groups"."id" = "group_users"."group_id" WHERE "group_users"."user_id" = 1242 AND (groups.id > 0) AND ( groups.id IN (
   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE visibility_level = 0

   UNION ALL

   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE visibility_level = 1
      AND 1239 IS NOT NULL

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1239
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 2

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
LEFT JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1239 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 3
      AND (gu.id IS NOT NULL OR FALSE)

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1239 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 4
 )
) AND (groups.id > 0) AND ( groups.id IN (
   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE members_visibility_level = 0

   UNION ALL

   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE members_visibility_level = 1
      AND 1239 IS NOT NULL

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1239
    WHERE g.members_visibility_level = 2

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
LEFT JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1239 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.members_visibility_level = 3
      AND (gu.id IS NOT NULL OR FALSE)

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1239 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.members_visibility_level = 4
 )
) ORDER BY "groups"."id" ASC, name ASC
